parameters: Talib_face
\n<Spearman>...well look who finally decides to show up...
Nika_face
\n<Nika>Heh. We only had to evade the nobles and their
religious fanatics. Halfway across the waste and we
got ambushed by some the lackeys sent by the Federation
of Peace....
Daric_face
\n<Daric>Yeah, Talib. I thought we weren't going to make it
more than a couple of times back there.
Talib_face
\n<Talib>Well no one's going to hold your hand around
here. \!How else are you supposed to get good at taking
them on if I'm with you all the time. \!I sent you
over to Paul to get you new recruits good training!
Talib_face
\n<Talib>You forget that being a warrior is one thing, but
learning to put down your weapons and use other things
like your wits is more difficult...
Talib_face
\n<Talib>..but no matter how difficult, it's worth sharpening
your mind, Nika!
Nika_face
\n<Nika>Well, enough with the old man phrases...I'm hungry.
Daric_face
\n<Daric>Yeah, I'm ready for some food too. \!No doubt that
Kilani will have something good waiting for us....
Talib_face
\n<Talib>Ha! When are you not hungry, Daric?
Daric_face
\n<Daric>Well....I'm usually hungry but after all that I'm a
little more hungry than usual!
Nika_face
\n<Nika>Yeah no kidding...leading them on a false trail to
the South is tiresome when you have to run around
and get back on your original path East. It felt
like we were running half-way across the planet.
Talib_face
\n<Talib>You young ones with your ever wandering imaginations...
Talib_face
\n<Talib>Well, let's head back to camp. I'm ready for something
to eat as well. \!...and yes, Daric. Kilani does have a nice
surprise for you...
Daric_face
\n<Daric>Oh yeah...
Nika_face
\n<Nika>Seriously, Daric? \!You're not going to die of hunger
that quickly...\!we just came from Paul's place before
making our way out here and you ate there as well!
Jenny even made you second helpings.
Daric_face
\n<Daric>Well I'm hungry so....let's get to camp!
Talib_face
\n<Talib>Well, alright then. Off we go.
